org.sqlproc.engine.impl
Class SqlMetaIdentItem

java.lang.Object
  org.sqlproc.engine.impl.SqlMetaIdentItem

 class SqlMetaIdentItem
extends java.lang.Object

A META SQL sub-element. A partial item for a SqlMetaIdent. It represents the name of an attribute in the input class (the static parameters class). In case there're more names, the input classes are embedded one in other.

Author:
Vladimir Hudec
